### Shader Architecture

#### Vertex Shader (GLSL 330)
```glsl
#version 330 core
layout (location = 0) in vec3 a_position;
layout (location = 1) in vec3 a_velocity;
layout (location = 2) in float a_lifetime;

uniform mat4 mvp_matrix;
uniform float particle_size;
uniform vec3 particle_color;
uniform float time;
uniform float audio_bass;
uniform float audio_mid;
uniform float audio_treble;

out vec3 v_position;
out float v_lifetime;

void main() {
    // Transform particle position
    vec4 world_pos = vec4(a_position, 1.0);
    gl_Position = mvp_matrix * world_pos;
    
    // Apply size modulation from audio
    float size_mod = 1.0 + audio_bass * 0.5;
    gl_PointSize = particle_size * size_mod;
    
    v_position = a_position;
    v_lifetime = a_lifetime;
}
```

#### Fragment Shader (GLSL 330)
```glsl
#version 330 core
in vec3 v_position;
in float v_lifetime;
out vec4 frag_color;

uniform vec3 particle_color;
uniform float time;

void main() {
    // Simple particle rendering with lifetime fade
    float alpha = v_lifetime * 0.8;
    frag_color = vec4(particle_color, alpha);
    
    // Add some visual interest with position-based color
    float dist = length(v_position);
    vec3 color = particle_color * (1.0 + dist * 0.2);
    frag_color.rgb = mix(particle_color, color, 0.3);
}
```

## Parameters (0.0-10.0 range)

### System Parameters
- **num_particles**: Number of active particles (0.0-50.0, representing 0-50,000 particles)
- **particle_size**: Base particle size in pixels (0.0-10.0)
- **particle_color**: Base particle color (0.0-10.0, mapped to RGB)
- **lifetime**: Base particle lifetime in seconds (0.0-10.0)
- **gravity**: Gravity force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **wind**: Wind force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **attractor_strength**: Attractor force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **repeller_strength**: Repeller force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **magnetic_strength**: Magnetic force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **noise_strength**: Noise force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **flocking_separation**: Separation force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **flocking_alignment**: Alignment force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **flocking_cohesion**: Cohesion force strength (0.0-10.0)
- **camera_distance**: Camera distance from origin (0.0-10.0)
- **camera_fov**: Camera field of view in degrees (0.0-10.0)
- **camera_rotation_x**: Camera X rotation in degrees (0.0-10.0)
- **camera_rotation_y**: Camera Y rotation in degrees (0.0-10.0)
- **mix**: Blend factor with input texture (0.0-10.0)

### Emitter Parameters (per-emitter, but exposed as system parameters)
- **emit_rate**: Particles per second (0.0-10.0)
- **emit_lifetime**: Particle lifetime (0.0-10.0)
- **emit_size**: Particle size (0.0-10.0)
- **emit_spread**: Initial velocity spread (0.0-10.0)

